      Purpose:     Process the web request.
      Parameters:  <none>
      Notes:       
    ------------------------------------------------------------------------------*/
  
    DEFINE VARIABLE lc-CustomerInfo     AS CHARACTER         NO-UNDO.

    {lib/checkloggedin.i}


    ASSIGN 
